<pre><code>&lt;mx:Application xmlns:mx="http://www.adobe.com/2006/mxml" layout="absolute" minWidth="955" minHeight="600"&gt;     &lt;mx:Script&gt;         &lt;![CDATA[                            protected function button1_clickHandler(event:MouseEvent):void             {                 var str:String = textId.text;             }                        ]]&gt;     &lt;/mx:Script&gt;     &lt;mx:VBox&gt;                    &lt;mx:HBox&gt;         &lt;mx:TextArea id="textId" restrict="^\r"/&gt;     &lt;/mx:HBox&gt;     &lt;mx:HBox&gt;         &lt;mx:Button label="Click Here" click="button1_clickHandler(event)" /&gt;     &lt;/mx:HBox&gt;     &lt;/mx:VBox&gt; &lt;/mx:Application&gt; </code></pre>  <p>first enter text as: "hi<code>\n</code>" in text area, see the text in textId.text by clicking button. Now delete the last character so text is "hi". but in textId.text still result showing as "hi<code>\n</code>". The new line at the end is not deleted.</p>